Package org.graffiti.plugins.ios.exporters.graphml

This package provides a plugin for writing Graphs to files using the graphML format.

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Base64
    Encodes and decodes to and from Base64 notation.
    Base64.InputStream
    A Base64.InputStream will read data from another InputStream, given in the constructor, and encode/decode to/from Base64 notation on the fly.
    Base64.OutputStream
    A Base64.OutputStream will write data to another OutputStream, given in the constructor, and encode/decode to/from Base64 notation on the fly.
    GraphMLgzWriter  
    GraphMLWriter
    Class GraphMLWriter is the main class for writing a graph to a graphML file.
    GraphMLWriterPlugin
    The plugin class for the graphML writing package.
